title: Greedy Guns v1.04
description: Greedy Guns is a joyful, color-filled platformer that sprinkles elements of exploration on top of excruciating challenges. This arcadey, twin-stick shooter rampage will leave you crying tears of joy  or defeat.Inspired by classic shooters like Gunstar Heroes, Metal Slug, and Contra, Greedy Guns brings the run-and-gun formula into the 21st Century!StoryHOLO CORP  a ubiquitous corporate behemoth that (obviously) values profit over ethics.
